      "message": "Remind me, is this the same as,\n\n  SkASSERT(SkToBool(this-\u003etoXYZD50()));\n\n?  I ask because\n\n1)  type() seems like something we want to delete rather than promote to SkColorSpace\n2)  we seem to dereference this-\u003etoXYZD50() without a null check\n\nMight be we actually want to do something a bit more defensive, like call\n\n  SkMatrix44 gamut;\n  if (!this-\u003etoXZYD50(\u0026gamut)) {\n     return error of some sort;\n  }\n  ...",
